    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to not-assessed in accordance with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. A limitation regarding non-Newtonian blood rheology at low shear rates was identified during the assessment; the risk is considered acceptable and the model is accepted for the stated COU.",
